_search_en.title: Hyejin Band
_search_en.description: Performance by jazz vocalist Hyejin Band. Hyejin, known for her solid skills and distinctive vocal color, trained in traditional jazz in New York and has released four studio albums and a vocal ensemble album. She performs with Park Min-sun (piano) known for her brilliant technique, Jeon Jae-geun (bass) with delicate interpretations, Lee Kwang-hyeok (drums) with vibrant energy, and Yeo Hyeon-woo (saxophone) with powerful phrasing, delivering a high-density interplay. The stage will present a moving performance imbued with Hyejin's unique emotion and narrative. Advance KRW 25,000, Door KRW 30,000.
